### Which sepal length is longer?

![Source: [Embedded Robotics](https://www.embedded-robotics.com/iris-dataset-classification/)](images/iris.png){fig-alt="Photographs of three iris species -- setosa, versicolor, and virginica -- showing differences in sepal and petal shape"}

